## ReadLammpsTraj
- Read lammps dump trajectory

### Installation

- github:

  ```bash
  git clone https://github.com/eastsheng/ReadLammpsTraj
  cd ReadLammpsTraj
  pip install .
  
  # or
  
  pip install git+https://github.com/eastsheng/ReadLammpsTraj.git
  ```

- pip

  ```bash
  pip install ReadLammpsTraj
  ```

  

### Usage

```python
